<div class="nbunit" id="16Nov1922"><font color="red">16 November 1922</font>, <cite>BLHW</cite> (JJ to Harriet Weaver): I stopped overnight in Lyon and telephoned to Mr Darantiere to meet me on the platform at Dijon. He took the same view as I did about the changes against the second edition</div>
